<br>
1&gt;Can only be hit with magical attacks (includes magic weapons)<br>
2&gt;max hit is 43<br>
3&gt;max proc is 143 (seems to proc like weapons do)<br>
4&gt;max kick/bash is 25<br>
5<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START >D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/grin.gif ALT=">D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> S is a 36 point DS<br>
6&gt;Stun is 6 seconds, does around 80 damage, and IS RESISTABLE!!!!!!<br>
<br>
Now some Normal stats<br>
only change thus far is it does up to 67 damage<br>
<br>
The pet is a level 49 pet and does not have a DD or Root ability.  it does seem to be simply a buffed up air pet (boo verant).  This is not our MAX level pet we can get but it certainly is the most damaging.  Max level summon pet is 50 with a staff of mastery.<br>
<br>
The pet is lacking in several areas but seems to do alright.  I will be working on tracking additional normal combat information and post it once I have gathered enough data.<br>
<br>
1 last thing.  This pet does rock.  I was in a seb group and my pet was killing 2 mobs to the rest of the groups 1 mob (no DD's being cast).  We had a warrior and shadowknight.  So yes the pet does outdamage a lot of PC's or so it seems.<br>
<br>
Dramira<br>
